				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><script>function mfTempOpenSection(id){var block=document.getElementById("mf-section-"+id);block.className+=" open-block";block.previousSibling.className+=" open-block";}</script><div role="note" class="hatnote">This article is about the programming language. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Inform_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Inform (disambiguation)">Inform (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
